                0.149
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "一、填空题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.156,
                0.318,
                0.188
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 \\(\\frac{\\mathrm{e}^{x + y} - y\\sin(xy)}{x\\sin(xy) - \\mathrm{e}^{x + y}}.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.089,
                0.195,
                0.454,
                0.208
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\mathrm{e}^{x + y} + \\cos (xy) = 0\\) 两边对 \\(x\\) 求导得"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.089,
                0.218,
                0.71,
                0.248
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(\\mathrm{e}^{x + y}\\cdot \\left(1 + \\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}}\\right) - \\sin (xy)\\cdot \\left(y + x\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}}\\right) = 0\\) ，解得 \\(\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}} = \\frac{\\mathrm{e}^{x + y} - y\\sin(xy)}{x\\sin(xy) - \\mathrm{e}^{x + y}}.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.059,
                0.257,
                0.31,
                0.285
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 \\(\\left\\{\\frac{2}{9}, \\frac{4}{9}, -\\frac{4}{9}\\right\\}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.089,
                0.295,
                0.705,
                0.325
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial x} = \\frac{2x}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}, \\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial y} = \\frac{2y}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}, \\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial z} = \\frac{2z}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2},\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.089,
                0.334,
                0.752,
                0.363
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(\\left.\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial x}\\right|_{M} = \\frac{2}{9},\\quad \\left.\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial y}\\right|_{M} = \\frac{4}{9},\\quad \\left.\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial z}\\right|_{M} = -\\frac{4}{9}\\) 则 \\(\\mathbf{grad}u\\Big|_M = \\left\\{\\frac{2}{9},\\frac{4}{9}, - \\frac{4}{9}\\right\\} .\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.059,
                0.373,
                0.203,
                0.401
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(3)【答案】 \\(\\frac{\\pi^2}{2}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.089,
                0.41,
                0.47,
                0.424
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(f(x)\\) 的傅里叶级数在 \\(x = \\pi\\) 处收敛于"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.284,
                0.432,
                0.741,
                0.462
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\frac {f (\\pi - 0) + f (\\pi + 0)}{2} = \\frac {f (\\pi - 0) + f (- \\pi + 0)}{2} = \\frac {\\pi^ {2}}{2}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.058,
                0.469,
                0.461,
                0.485
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(4)【答案】 \\( y = (x + C)\\cos x \\) （\\( C \\) 为任意常数）."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.088,
                0.491,
                0.487,
                0.504
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 微分方程 \\( y' + y \\tan x = \\cos x \\) 的通解为"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.205,
                0.511,
                0.814,
                0.537
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(y = \\left(\\int \\cos x\\cdot \\mathrm{e}^{\\int \\tan x\\mathrm{d}x}\\mathrm{d}x + C\\right)\\cdot \\mathrm{e}^{-\\int \\tan x\\mathrm{d}x} = (x + C)\\cos x(C\\) 为任意常数）."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.059,
                0.547,
                0.185,
                0.561
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（5）【答案】1."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.088,
                0.568,
                0.61,
                0.583
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】方法一 因为 \\(\\mathbf{A}\\) 的任意两行都成比例，所以 \\(r(\\mathbf{A})\\leqslant 1\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.089,
                0.59,
                0.46,
                0.604
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "又因为 \\(\\mathbf{A} \\neq \\mathbf{0}\\), 所以 \\(r(\\mathbf{A}) \\geqslant 1\\), 故 \\(r(\\mathbf{A}) = 1\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.612,
                0.151,
                0.625
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "方法二"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.088,
                0.633,
                0.602,
                0.714
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\mathbf {A} = \\left[ \\begin{array}{c} {a _ {1}} \\\\ {a _ {2}} \\\\ {\\vdots} \\\\ {a _ {n}} \\end{array} \\right] (b _ {1}, b _ {2}, \\dots , b _ {n}) = \\pmb {\\alpha} \\pmb {\\beta} ^ {\\mathrm {T}}, \\text {其 中} \\pmb {\\alpha} = \\left[ \\begin{array}{c} {a _ {1}} \\\\ {a _ {2}} \\\\ {\\vdots} \\\\ {a _ {n}} \\end{array} \\right], \\pmb {\\beta} = \\left[ \\begin{array}{c} {b _ {1}} \\\\ {b _ {2}} \\\\ {\\vdots} \\\\ {b _ {n}} \\end{array} \\right],\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.089,
                0.722,
                0.34,
                0.736
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nr (\\mathbf {A}) = r (\\boldsymbol {\\alpha} \\boldsymbol {\\beta} ^ {\\mathrm {T}}) \\leqslant r (\\boldsymbol {\\alpha}) = 1,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.088,
                0.745,
                0.707,
                0.759
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "再由 \\(a_{i}\\neq 0,b_{i}\\neq 0,i = 1,2,\\dots ,n\\) 得 \\(\\mathbf{A}\\neq \\mathbf{O}\\) ，于是 \\(r(A)\\geqslant 1\\) ，故 \\(r(A) = 1\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.058,
                0.766,
                0.147,
                0.781
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "二、选择题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.058,
                0.787,
                0.206,
                0.801
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 (D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.808,
                0.777,
                0.841
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 1^{-}}\\frac{x^2 - 1}{x - 1}\\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{1}{x - 1}} = 2\\lim_{x\\to 1^{-}}\\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{1}{x - 1}} = 0,\\) \\(\\lim_{x\\to 1^{+}}\\frac{x^2 - 1}{x - 1}\\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{1}{x - 1}} = 2\\lim_{x\\to 1^{+}}\\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{1}{x - 1}} = +\\infty ,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.089,
                0.847,
                0.456,
                0.875
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "得 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 1}\\frac{x^2 - 1}{x - 1}\\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{1}{x - 1}}\\) 不存在但不是 \\(\\infty\\) ，应选(D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.058,
                0.884,
                0.205,
                0.898
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（2）【答案】 (C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.905,
                0.531,
                0.935
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\left|(-1)^n\\left(1 - \\cos \\frac{\\alpha}{n}\\right)\\right| = 2\\sin^2\\frac{\\alpha}{2n} \\sim \\frac{\\alpha^2}{2} \\cdot \\frac{1}{n^2},\\)"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.07,
                0.876,
                0.125
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\(\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\frac{\\alpha^2}{2} \\cdot \\frac{1}{n^2}\\) 收敛，所以 \\(\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\left| (-1)^n \\left(1 - \\cos \\frac{\\alpha}{n}\\right) \\right|\\) 收敛，即 \\(\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} (-1)^n \\left(1 - \\cos \\frac{\\alpha}{n}\\right)\\) 绝对收敛，应选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.132,
                0.201,
                0.147
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（3）【答案】 （B）."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.083,
                0.153,
                0.467,
                0.168
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 曲线的切线向量为 \\(\\pmb{T} = \\{1, -2t, 3t^2\\}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.178,
                0.926,
                0.204
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(\\{1, -2t, 3t^2\\} \\cdot \\{1, 2, 1\\} = 0\\) 得 \\(t_1 = \\frac{1}{3}, t_2 = 1\\)，故与平面 \\(x + 2y + z = 4\\) 平行的切线有2条，应选(B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.213,
                0.201,
                0.228
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（4）【答案】 (C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.234,
                0.586,
                0.272
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(f(x) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}2x^{3}, & x < 0,\\\\ 4x^{3}, & x\\geqslant 0, \\end{array} \\right.\\) \\(f^{\\prime}(x) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}6x^{2}. & x < 0,\\\\ 12x^{2}, & x > 0, \\end{array} \\right.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.281,
                0.53,
                0.315
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "显然 \\(f^{\\prime}(0) = f^{\\prime \\prime}(0) = 0\\) ， \\(f''(x) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}12x, & x <   0,\\\\ 24x, & x\\geqslant 0, \\end{array} \\right.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.322,
                0.55,
                0.355
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nf _ {-} ^ {\\prime \\prime} (0) = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0 ^ {-}} \\frac {f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (x)}{x} = 1 2, \\quad f _ {+} ^ {\\prime \\prime} (0) = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0 ^ {+}} \\frac {f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (x)}{x} = 2 4,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.361,
                0.645,
                0.376
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为 \\(f_{-}^{\\prime \\prime}(0)\\neq f_{+}^{\\prime \\prime}(0)\\) ，所以 \\(f^{(n)}(0)\\) 存在的最高阶数 \\(n = 2\\) ，应选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.384,
                0.203,
                0.398
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（5）【答案】 （A)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.054,
                0.405,
                0.926,
                0.461
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】因为 \\(\\xi_{1}\\) 与 \\(\\xi_{2}\\) 线性无关，所以三元齐次线性方程组 \\(AX = 0\\) 的基础解系中至少含2个解向量，即 \\(3 - r(A)\\geqslant 2\\) ，得 \\(r(\\mathbf{A})\\leqslant 1\\) ，而选项(B)(C)(D)中矩阵的秩都大于1，所以均不对，只有选项（A）正确.三、"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.469,
                0.639,
                0.497
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【解】由 \\( 1 - \\sqrt{1 - x^2} = -[(1 - x^2)^{\\frac{1}{2}} - 1] \\sim \\frac{1}{2} x^2 (x \\to 0) \\)，得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.507,
                0.744,
                0.551
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - \\sin x - 1}{1 - \\sqrt {1 - x ^ {2}}} = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - \\sin x - 1}{\\frac {1}{2} x ^ {2}} = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - \\cos x}{x} = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} (\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} + \\sin x) = 1.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.561,
                0.377,
                0.588
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【解】 \\(\\frac{\\partial z}{\\partial x} = f_1' \\cdot \\mathrm{e}^x \\sin y + 2xf_2'\\),"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.598,
                0.793,
                0.664
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} \\frac {\\partial^ {2} z}{\\partial x \\partial y} = e ^ {x} \\sin y \\cdot \\left(f _ {1 1} ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\cdot e ^ {x} \\cos y + 2 y f _ {1 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime}\\right) + f _ {1} ^ {\\prime} \\cdot e ^ {x} \\cos y + 2 x \\left(f _ {2 1} ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\cdot e ^ {x} \\cos y + 2 y f _ {2 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime}\\right) \\\\ = \\frac {1}{2} e ^ {2 x} \\sin 2 y \\cdot f _ {1 1} ^ {\\prime \\prime} + 2 e ^ {x} (y \\sin y + x \\cos y) f _ {1 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime} + f _ {1} ^ {\\prime} \\cdot e ^ {x} \\cos y + 4 x y f _ {2 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.673,
                0.571,
                0.699
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(3)【解】 \\(\\int_{1}^{3} f(x - 2) \\, \\mathrm{d}x = \\int_{1}^{3} f(x - 2) \\, \\mathrm{d}(x - 2) = \\int_{-1}^{1} f(x) \\, \\mathrm{d}x\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.268,
                0.709,
                0.595,
                0.736
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= \\int_ {- 1} ^ {0} (1 + x ^ {2}) \\mathrm {d} x + \\int_ {0} ^ {1} \\mathrm {e} ^ {- x} \\mathrm {d} x = \\frac {7}{3} - \\frac {1}{\\mathrm {e}}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.055,
                0.745,
                0.616,
                0.76
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "四、【解】 特征方程为 \\(\\lambda^2 + 2\\lambda - 3 = 0\\)，特征根为 \\(\\lambda_1 = -3, \\lambda_2 = 1\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.767,
                0.487,
                0.782
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(y^{\\prime \\prime} + 2y^{\\prime} - 3y = 0\\) 的通解为 \\(y = C_1\\mathrm{e}^{-3x} + C_2\\mathrm{e}^x\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.791,
                0.658,
                0.817
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "令 \\(y^{\\prime \\prime} + 2y^{\\prime} - 3y = \\mathrm{e}^{-3x}\\) 的特解为 \\(y_0(x) = ax\\mathrm{e}^{-3x}\\) ，代入得 \\(a = -\\frac{1}{4}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.081,
                0.826,
                0.362,
                0.841
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(y^{\\prime \\prime} + 2y^{\\prime} - 3y = \\mathrm{e}^{-3x}\\) 的通解为"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.29,
                0.85,
                0.717,
                0.876
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(y = C_{1}\\mathrm{e}^{-3x} + C_{2}\\mathrm{e}^{x} - \\frac{1}{4} x\\mathrm{e}^{-3x}(C_{1},C_{2}\\) 为任意常数）."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.053,
                0.885,
                0.473,
                0.9
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "五、【解】补充 \\(\\Sigma_{1}:z = 0(x^{2} + y^{2}\\leqslant a^{2})\\) ，取下侧，"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.156,
                0.907,
                0.663,
                0.939
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nI = \\iint_ {\\Sigma} (x ^ {3} + a z ^ {2}) d y d z + (y ^ {3} + a x ^ {2}) d z d x + (z ^ {3} + a y ^ {2}) d x d y\n\\]"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.18,
                0.071,
                0.756,
                0.107
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= \\left(\\iint_ {\\Sigma + \\Sigma_ {1}} - \\iint_ {\\Sigma_ {1}}\\right) (x ^ {3} + a z ^ {2}) d y d z + (y ^ {3} + a x ^ {2}) d z d x + (z ^ {3} + a y ^ {2}) d x d y,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.089,
                0.111,
                0.59,
                0.147
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "而 \\(\\iint_{\\Sigma + \\Sigma_1} (x^3 + az^2) \\, \\mathrm{d}y \\, \\mathrm{d}z + (y^3 + ax^2) \\, \\mathrm{d}z \\, \\mathrm{d}x + (z^3 + ay^2) \\, \\mathrm{d}x \\, \\mathrm{d}y\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.089,
                0.111,
                0.643,
                0.301
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} = 3 \\iiint_ {\\Omega} \\left(x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}\\right) \\mathrm {d} v = 3 \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\pi} \\mathrm {d} \\theta \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} \\mathrm {d} \\varphi \\int_ {0} ^ {a} r ^ {4} \\sin \\varphi \\mathrm {d} r = \\frac {6 \\pi}{5} a ^ {5}, \\\\ \\iint_ {x _ {1}} \\left(x ^ {3} + a z ^ {2}\\right) d y d z + \\left(y ^ {3} + a x ^ {2}\\right) d z d x + \\left(z ^ {3} + a y ^ {2}\\right) d x d y \\\\ = \\iint_ {\\Sigma_ {1}} a y ^ {2} d x d y = - a \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant a ^ {2}} y ^ {2} d x d y = - \\frac {a}{2} \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant a ^ {2}} (x ^ {2} + y ^ {2}) d x d y \\\\ = - \\frac {a}{2} \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\pi} \\mathrm {d} \\theta \\int_ {0} ^ {a} r ^ {3} \\mathrm {d} r = - \\frac {\\pi}{4} a ^ {5}, \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.086,
                0.31,
                0.791,
                0.343
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(\\iint_{\\Sigma} (x^3 + az^2) \\, \\mathrm{d}y \\, \\mathrm{d}z + (y^3 + ax^2) \\, \\mathrm{d}z \\, \\mathrm{d}x + (z^3 + ay^2) \\, \\mathrm{d}x \\, \\mathrm{d}y = \\frac{6\\pi}{5} a^5 + \\frac{\\pi}{4} a^5 = \\frac{29}{20}\\pi a^5.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.057,
                0.347,
                0.521,
                0.362
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "六、【解】 不妨设 \\(0 < x_{1} < x_{2}\\)，由拉格朗日中值定理得"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
